Package: montyhall
Type: Package
Title: Package creates a new Monty Hall Problem game.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Victor Vega
Maintainer: Victor Vega <vvega10@asu.edu>
Description: A contestant is has three doors to choose from, one has a car and
    the other two have goats. The contestant picks a door, the host reveals a
    goat door and gives the contestant the option to switch their initial door 
    to the remaining closed door. The package allows you to simulate and test
    which strategy yields the best chance of winning the car.
Depends:
    dplyr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
